Yelp's Jeremy Stoppelman: a profile
SUNDAY PROFILE: Jeremy Stoppelman


By Julian Guthrie


        Updated 3:07 am, Monday, July 16, 2012
    





































































































































































































































































































                                            Photo: Russell Yip, The Chronicle
                                    
 


